				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/Bi%C3%AAn-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-v%C4%83n-H%E1%BB%93-gi%C3%A0-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem--rZ20MM4vXnPhx9WPQmsVA">Biên thượng văn Hồ già kỳ 3 - 邊上聞胡笳其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/author-3vzgm_fq7JLuFBSuENsFJw">Đỗ Mục</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%BAc/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-ho%E1%BA%A1-k%C3%AA-%C4%91%E1%BB%93/poem-2-rafZwTwspWqpLenBYd2w">Đề hoạ kê đồ - 題畫鷄闓</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%BAc/author-DYGad0thHvgCxK3Szp1zVQ">Trần Đình Túc</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng-%C4%90%E1%BA%ADu-L%C6%B0-phong-di-ch%E1%BB%A7-kh%C3%A1ch-L%C3%BD-vi%C3%AAn-ngo%E1%BA%A1i-t%E1%BB%AD-Ph%E1%BB%89-tri-t%E1%BB%B1-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-bwdpLyVV0PX9-qMG09KQtw">Đồng Đậu Lư phong di chủ khách Lý viên ngoại tử Phỉ, tri tự vận - 同豆盧峰貽主客李員外 子棐知字韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/Giang-H%E1%BA%A1-t%E1%BA%B7ng-Vi-Nam-L%C4%83ng-B%C4%83ng/poem-yb9zvaigGyllqbC7S0M7qQ">Giang Hạ tặng Vi Nam Lăng Băng - 江夏贈韋南陵冰</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%BD-B%E1%BA%A1ch/author-8WYDeeki5xZo8eD-k6Sk5A">Lý Bạch</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BA%A9m-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-Ti%E1%BB%81m/H%C3%A1n-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-h%C3%A0nh/poem-mSH9PE5CreDWAB83y1xujw">Hán tướng hành - 漢將行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%E1%BA%A9m-%C4%90%E1%BB%A9c-Ti%E1%BB%81m/author-RNpImmo2Zi_8n8IJeKR5eg">Thẩm Đức Tiềm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-V%E1%BA%A1n-L%C3%BD/S%C3%A1p-%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-ca/poem-aRKGLIS3fXEdf4EiJ2Kk3A">Sáp ương ca - 插秧歌</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-V%E1%BA%A1n-L%C